Package: cfma
Type: Package
Title: Causal Functional Mediation Analysis
Version: 1.0
Date: 2018-05-16
Author: Yi Zhao <zhaoyi1026@gmail.com>, Xi Luo
        <xi.rossi.luo@gmail.com>, Martin Lindquist <mal2053@gmail.com>,
        Brian Caffo <bcaffo@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Yi Zhao <zhaoyi1026@gmail.com>
Description: Performs causal functional mediation analysis (CFMA) for
        functional treatment, functional mediator, and functional
        outcome. This package includes two functional mediation model
        types: (1) a concurrent mediation model and (2) a historical
        influence mediation model. See Zhao et al. (2018), Functional
        Mediation Analysis with an Application to Functional Magnetic
        Resonance Imaging Data, <arXiv:1805.06923> for details.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
NeedsCompilation: no
Packaged: 2018-05-22 14:15:59 UTC; yizhao
Repository: CRAN
Date/Publication: 2018-05-24 12:45:18 UTC
Additional_repositories: https://cranhaven.r-universe.dev
